Text.val: For Short positions the max quote difference kan exceed the maximum of 999999.99% which causes an ORA-ERROR: ORA-01438
Hence the minimum in the expression.
Only alert if previous wasn't already the maximum:

ExpSyntax.val: FlwMtr('Error service ''notifyQuoteUpdate'' : Fund alert already send! Notification not processed for : InstrumentId='&Str({1,2},VarPic('{1,2}'VAR,0))&' ContractId='&Str({0,23},VarPic('{0,23}'VAR,0))&' QuoteDate='&DStr({1,3},'YYYY-MM-DD'),'FALSE'LOG)
